{"tid":774403,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"食定唔食？食得起先好食！","createTime":"2018-08-10T09:50:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T10:17:03.000Z","uid":104965,"like":16,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6436313dc5bc59021321c0a2d5539c4f7050a642","tid":774403,"uid":104965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T09:50:24.000Z","msg":"朋友一直同女朋友相處2年一直好好<br />\n只係佢條女身材好一般<br />\n試問男人有邊個唔鐘意身材勁既女人呢<br />\n所以佢一直都想試下大波妹<br />\n但係又怕會傷害到條女<br />\n<br />\n到佢返左份新工<br />\n竟然有件尤物挑釁佢（我好撚羨慕）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有次機會佢差d 可以食埋<br />\n但係佢過唔到自己個關最後無食<br />\n<br />\n而家佢好煩惱應唔應該辭工<br />\n驚有日頂唔順同件尤物開波<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正評：辭職啦！咁好嘅女朋友要珍惜，唔好比機會自己犯錯<br />\n<br />\n負評：食左先啦！大波妹咁易食到架？"},{"pid":"1cdeae3da9f0f6663ef53299f8ee3c33a190c96b","tid":774403,"uid":46595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T09:51:20.000Z","msg":"純文字討論?"},{"pid":"9563d287232fa4d7cd16680a2886bffffceed4bf","tid":774403,"uid":158633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T09:52:13.000Z","msg":"你朋友就係你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8f0099f1c5694f89bd68ad9d3a1341e08d6e3c9","tid":774403,"uid":129221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T09:52:17.000Z","msg":"食左先辭咪得 當無野發生過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e14f66cdbba8a40ff87349f6b403fd773351aa","tid":774403,"uid":189243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T09:52:26.000Z","msg":"確定食完無手尾跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4c725e2011d59bbbdda94f35136a6eba705113b","tid":774403,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T09:52:31.000Z","msg":"雖然比咗正評<br />\n不過如果換轉係我 都係食咗先<im